data.description: BUYERS AGENTS WELCOME! Beautiful custom craftsman style home in the highly sought-after Five Forks area in Simpsonville, SC. Only 1 mile from Bells Crossing Elementary School and about 5 minutes from grocery and restaurants. Quiet Providence Square neighborhood with only 38 homes, a community park and pavilion with a fireplace for social gatherings. The front of the property looks out into the park in the center of the neighborhood and the rear looks into an undeveloped neighbors property.    Hardwoods on the first floor with wood accents throughout. Master on main and 3 more bedrooms upstairs including 2 bedrooms which share a  Jack and Jill bathroom. The third bedroom has an attached full bath and walk in closet with a storage that is accessed through the closet. There is also additional space upstairs for a bonus room which can be configured to the new owners specification. Back porch is built with a  durable Trex floor. Back yard is a blank pallet that's ready for your creative ideas specified to your taste. This home has a new roof (2023), new upstairs A/C (fall 2022) and newer downstairs A/C (2018), new Bosch dishwasher, new garbage disposal. Upgraded interior paint throughout. Paint matched storage shed in the back.
data.whatILove: This WELL BUILT beautiful CUSTOM home is situated in a SMALL QUIET community in the very popular FIVE FORKS area of Simpsonville South Carolina. It's situated near GREAT SCHOOLS. RESTAURANTS and GROCERIES are also just MINUTES AWAY. NEW features include; NEW ROOF (2023), NEW WATER HEATER (2023), NEW UPSATAIRS HVAC (2022), NEW DOWNSATAIRS HVAC (2018), NEW DISHWASHER (2021), NEW GARBAGE DISPOSAL (2022), NEWLY RENOVATED CRAWLSPACE with DEHUMIDIFIER (2021) & FRESH PAINT THROUGHOUT.
